name: Armiryle the Starguide Dragon
desc:
2 Effect Monsters
Cannot be used as Link Material. You can target 1 face-up monster this card points to; Special Summon 1 monster from your hand in Defense Position, with the same original Level as that monster, to your zone this card points to, but negate its effects. You can only use this effect of "Armiryle the Starguide Dragon" once per turn.
